1 print out a welcome massage
2 ask to print out instructions to the game
    2.1 if^ yes then print out instructions
3 ask user if they still wants to play
    3.1 if no then print exit message and exit the game
4 ask for the range of number to be guessed
5 ask for number of guesses user will have to guess right
6 have code pick a number
7 user guess the number
8 compare the user guess to computer picked number
9 give user hint if guess is less then or more then
10 user get 'numberOf_guesses' chances to guess (loop)
11 if guessed right print victory massage
12 if guessed wrong more times then 'user_max_guesses' print losing massage
13 print exit massage

